*`<st c="27301">`{=html} Art is one of the means of unifying people.`</st>`{=html}*

`<st c="27345">`{=html} If beautiful art does not express moral ideas, ideas which unite people, then it is not art, but only entertainment. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="27463">`{=html}People need to be entertained in order to distance themselves from disappointment in their lives.`</st>`{=html}

