### ***`<st c="28262">`{=html} February 29`</st>`{=html}*** {#006.html_february29}

![Image](ops/images/img01_044.jpg)

`<st c="28274">`{=html} To move, you must know where to go, in terms both of everyday motion and of your whole life. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="28368">`{=html}In order to live a good life, you must know where life leads.`</st>`{=html}

*`<st c="28429">`{=html} Perfection is of God. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="28452">`{=html}To wish for perfection is of man.`</st>`{=html}*

`<st c="28485">`{=html} ---JOHANN WOLFGANG VON GOETHE`</st>`{=html}

`<st c="28513">`{=html} Life is not given to us that we might live idly without work. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="28576">`{=html}No, our life is a struggle and a journey. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="28618">`{=html}Good should struggle with evil; truth should struggle with falsehood; freedom should struggle with slavery; love should struggle with hatred. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="28760">`{=html}Life is movement, a walk along the way of life to the fulfillment of those ideas which illuminate us, both in our intellect and in our hearts, with divine light.`</st>`{=html}

`<st c="28921">`{=html} ---After GIUSEPPE MAZZINI`</st>`{=html}

`<st c="28945">`{=html} The ideal is within you, and the obstacle to reaching this ideal is also within you. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="29031">`{=html}You already possess all the material from which to create your ideal self.`</st>`{=html}

`<st c="29105">`{=html} ---THOMAS CARLYLE`</st>`{=html}

`<st c="29121">`{=html} We should believe that the goodness which exists in us and in this world will be fulfilled. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="29214">`{=html}This is the major condition to make it happen.`</st>`{=html}[]{#006.html_page_72}

