`<st c="5236">`{=html} Love of God is love in itself; it is love for the sake of love. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="5301">`{=html}This kind of love is the highest blessing. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="5344">`{=html}It does not allow the slightest possibility of treating even a single creature without love; if there is even one person whom you do not love, then you lose God's love and blessing.`</st>`{=html}

