`<st c="5730">`{=html} Some say that you should be afraid of God. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="5774">`{=html}Not true; you have to love God. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="5806">`{=html}How can you love those whom you are afraid of? `</st>`{=html}`<st c="5853">`{=html}God is love, and how can you be afraid of love? `</st>`{=html}`<st c="5901">`{=html}No, you should not fear God, but love Him. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="5944">`{=html}And if you love God, then you will not be afraid of Him, or anything else in the world.`</st>`{=html}[]{#007.html_page_78}


