`<st c="6039">`{=html} Physical work, physical exercise for your body, is a necessary condition of life. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="6122">`{=html}A man can force others to do things for him, but he cannot free himself from the necessity of his own physical work. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="6239">`{=html}And if a man does not work at necessary and good things, then he will work at unnecessary and stupid things.`</st>`{=html}

`<st c="6347">`{=html} Work, the process of work in itself, is the most important thing for us, and its reward should be of minor importance; if it is, you please your creator, God. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="6507">`{=html}If the reward is of major importance for you, and the work itself of minor importance, then you are the slave of the reward and its creator, the devil, and even the lowest and the least among all devils.`</st>`{=html}

