`<st c="7190">`{=html} So that this exercise may give you joy and satisfaction, do good physical work. `</st>`{=html}`<st c="7271">`{=html}This is also the best way to serve others.`</st>`{=html}[]{#007.html_page_79}


### ***`<st c="7313">`{=html} March 8`</st>`{=html}*** {#007.html_march8}

